        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "The Zend_View_Helper_Action has no exception Handling.  If an exception is thrown in the action, and caught - the view renderer object never gets set back into place.\n\nI wrote a little patch around the issue - it just catches the exception in the dispatch, and throws the same exception after setting the view stuff back to the original state."
        },
